Class CommandResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.igeekinc.firehose.CommandResult

  • public class CommandResult
extends java.lang.Object
    CommandResult is returned from the command processing code in the server to the Firehose framework. It contains all of the information to be returned to the client
